## Configuration Example

### pyproject.toml
```toml
[tool.black]
line-length = 88
target-version = ['py39']

[tool.mypy]
python_version = "3.9"
warn_return_any = true
disallow_untyped_defs = true

[tool.pytest.ini_options]
testpaths = ["tests"]
addopts = "--cov=src --cov-report=html"
```

